data.description: ***HUGE END UNIT***Take advantage of this incredible opportunity! Discover this lovely light and bright 3 bedroom END UNIT townhome featuring almost 2000 square feet with tasteful stone accents, a meticulously maintained yard, an inviting front porch, and a convenient rear-entry 2-car garage. The living/dining room showcases high ceilings, a trending palette, and plush carpeting in all the right places. Gather loved ones in the family room with a cozy fireplace, perfect for creating intimate moments. The kitchen comes with raised panel cabinets, efficient recessed lighting, built-in appliances, a handy pantry, and a two-tier island with a breakfast bar for casual dining. The serene primary suite is bathed in natural light, complemented by an ensuite with dual vanities and a walk-in closet. Relax after a long day and enjoy the outdoors on the open patio. Make this yours today! ***This home has been HOME WARRANTY PRE-INSPECTED and comes with a Free 1 Year Buyer's Home Warranty! ***CHECK OUT THE 3D VIRTUAL OPEN HOUSE AND VIDEO ATTACHED TO THIS LISTING***
